      "rationale": "A systematic mesh refinement study using three element sizes (coarse, medium, fine) was performed. The Grid Convergence Index for construct stiffness is 0.7%, satisfying the Gradation 3 threshold. Contact zone mesh density was verified separately."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
