      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "rationale": "Standard operating procedures documented for model setup, boundary condition application, and post-processing. Two independent analysts reviewed model inputs. Gradation 2 achieved."
    },
    {
