    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment is Accepted at Medium assurance level. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is offset by the high relevance of the validation activities to the COU, the quantitative output comparison satisfying E/uval < 1.96 for all three QoIs, and the multi-laboratory experimental dataset. The model is considered fit for the intended regulatory purpose.",
